{"tid":1661841,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚飲大左 同最好朋友上左床","createTime":"2019-10-18T11:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T03:28:17.000Z","uid":1734,"like":12,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"147e4d1f8e9a4c11e4bc0af448b285b6465e6a18","tid":1661841,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾日女朋友去左深圳旅行 <br />\n所以屋企得番自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住尋晚，我沖完涼 <br />\n發覺電話有十幾個misscall <br />\n原來我朋友岩岩比男友飛左 <br />\n喊哂口咁同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後傾左成個鐘電話 <br />\n佢忽然話：不如出來陪我飲酒？ <br />\n但係個陣已經成十一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我見屋企無咩人 <br />\n又懶出去 <br />\n就話：不如你上來啦 我屋企又齊酒 <br />\n有私人空間又慳錢 <br />\n於是佢就上左來... <br />\n我地青島，生力，百威，藍妹 <br />\n咩都溝下來飲 <br />\n結果唔使一個鐘兩個已經醉醉地同好high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然 <br />\n佢對眼水汪汪咁問我： <br />\n你可唔可以 錫我一淡？ <br />\n可能真係能成為密友大概總帶著愛 <br />\n我竟然諗都無諗就錫左落去 <br />\n結果我地越咀越激 <br />\n互相纏住大家條頸 <br />\n舌頭交纏住咁行左入我房 <br />\n一攤上床 <br />\n我地互相摷左陣大家就埋牙 <br />\n詳細就唔多講 <br />\n只可以講係幾開心 <br />\n<br />\n唉 巴絲點算好 好驚無朋友做 自細踢開波  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0658449ea18c6795bae7e1444daa5f6b6cfb99ed","tid":1661841,"uid":1734,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"大家都出左兩次先訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc74ee2bdbc7a8bde61ba2ef2df284a2540f6f2","tid":1661841,"uid":47268,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:14:09.000Z","msg":"香港搞成咁樓主仲有心情開膠po<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等我用法術攻擊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"